name: Birds on Pebbles - Signed Archival Art Print in A4 or A3 Size
description:
This signed open edition giclée (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Giclee) art print feature two birds balancing on "pebbles".

The artwork was originally hand drawn by me. Approximate size of the art image itself is 5 x 8 inches (130 x 200 mm). This archival art print was printed using a professional quality, pigment ink printer (therefore creating crisp & waterproof colours) on mould-made (therefore strong), 250 gsm, off-white/light cream, lightly textured, 100% rag (cotton or linen) fine art paper. The size of the A4 paper is approximately 8 x 11.5 inches (or 210 x 297mm).

I try my best to portray the actual colors but please note that they may still slightly vary from those shown due to the nature of photographic/scanning processes and as well as, individual computer monitor settings.
